<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd">
<html>

    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <!-- Custom CSS Start --> 
    <style type="text/css">

@font-face {
  font-family: "BellSlim SemiBold";
  src: url(data:application/x-font-otf;charset=utf-8;base64,)
}</style>
    <!-- Custom CSS End --> 
    <style type="text/css">
      ReadMsgBody{ width: 100%;}
      .ExternalClass {width: 100%;}
      .ExternalClass, .ExternalClass p, .ExternalClass span, .ExternalClass font, .ExternalClass td, .ExternalClass div {line-height: 100%;}
      body {-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%;margin:0 !important;}
      p { margin: 1em 0;}
      table td { border-collapse: collapse;}
      img {outline:0;}
      a img {border:none;}
      @-ms-viewport{ width: device-width;}
    </style>
    <style type="text/css">
      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
        .container {width: 100% !important;}
        .footer { width:auto !important; margin-left:0; }
        .mobile-hidden { display:none !important; }
        .logo { display:block !important; padding:0 !important; }
        img { max-width:100% !important; height:auto !important; max-height:auto !important;}
        .header img{max-width:100% !important;height:auto !important; max-height:auto !important;}
        .photo img { width:100% !important; max-width:100% !important; height:auto !important;}
        .drop { display:block !important; width: 100% !important; float:left; clear:both;}
        .footerlogo { display:block !important; width: 100% !important; padding-top:15px; float:left; clear:both;}
        .nav4, .nav5, .nav6 { display: none !important; }
        .tableBlock {width:100% !important;}
        .responsive-td {width:100% !important; display:block !important; padding:0 !important; }
        .fluid, .fluid-centered {
          width: 100% !important;
          max-width: 100% !important;
          height: auto !important;
          margin-left: auto !important;
          margin-right: auto !important;
        }
        .fluid-centered {
          margin-left: auto !important;
          margin-right: auto !important;
        }
        /* MOBILE GLOBAL STYLES - DO NOT CHANGE */
        body { padding: 0px !important; font-size: 16px !important; line-height: 150% !important;}
        h1 { font-size: 22px !important; line-height: normal !important;}
        h2 { font-size: 20px !important; line-height: normal !important;}
        h3 { font-size: 18px !important; line-height: normal !important;}
        .buttonstyles {
          font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif !important;
          font-size: 16px !important;
          color: #FFFFFF !important;
          padding: 10px !important;
        }
        /* END OF MOBILE GLOBAL STYLES - DO NOT CHANGE */
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
        .container { width:100% !important; }
        .mobile-hidden { display:none !important; }
        .logo { display:block !important; padding:0 !important; }
        .photo img { width:100% !important; height:auto !important;}
        .nav5, .nav6 { display: none !important;}
        .fluid, .fluid-centered {
          width: 100% !important;
          max-width: 100% !important;
          height: auto !important;
          margin-left: auto !important;
          margin-right: auto !important;
        }
        .fluid-centered {
          margin-left: auto !important;
          margin-right: auto !important;
        }
      }
    </style>

data.code:
<script runat="server" language="JavaScript">
  //// https://mc-yfyyj2sjhsjhkwc1s8w4zrxx4.pub.sfmc-content.com/4riylizrw0l?f=slackEventSubscription.html&t=68b2-208-78-41-216

  Platform.Load("core", "1.1.1");
  HTTPHeader.SetValue("Access-Control-Allow-Methods", "GET, POST");
  HTTPHeader.SetValue("Access-Control-Allow-Origin", "*");
  HTTPHeader.SetValue(
    "Access-Control-Allow-Headers",
    "Content-Type, Access-Control-Allow-Headers, Authorization, X-Requested-With"
  );

  var userList = [];
  var channelList = [];
  try {
    var postBody = Platform.Request.GetPostData();
    var parsedData = Platform.Function.ParseJSON(postBody);
    if (parsedData.challenge) {
      Write('{"challenge":"' + parsedData.challenge + '"}');
    } else if (parsedData.action == "getUser") {
      var userListURL = "https://slack.com/api/users.list";
      var headerNames = ["Authorization"];
      var headerValues = [parsedData.bearer];
      var r = HTTP.Get(userListURL, headerNames, headerValues);
      //Write(r['Status']);
      var status = r["Status"];
      var content = Platform.Function.ParseJSON(r["Content"]);
      //Write('Total users found - ' + Stringify(content.members.length));
      if (content.ok == true) {
        for (var i = 0; i < content.members.length; i++) {
          //Write('\n' + content.members[i].is_bot)
          if (!content.members[i].is_bot && content.members[i].id != 'USLACKBOT') {
            userList.push({
              id: content.members[i].id,
              real_name: content.members[i].profile.real_name,
              team: content.members[i].profile.team
            });
          }
        }
      }
      //Write('\n final out ');
      Write(Stringify(userList));
    }else if (parsedData.action == "getChannel") {
      var channelListURL = "https://slack.com/api/conversations.list";
      var headerNames = ["Authorization"];
      var headerValues = [parsedData.bearer];
      var r = HTTP.Get(channelListURL, headerNames, headerValues);
      //Write(r['Status']);
      var status = r["Status"];
      var content = Platform.Function.ParseJSON(r["Content"]);
      //Write('Total users found - ' + Stringify(content));
      if (content.ok == true) {
        for (var i = 0; i < content.channels.length; i++) {
          //Write('\n' + content.members[i].is_bot)
          if (
            content.channels[i].is_channel == true &&
            content.channels[i].is_private == false &&
            content.channels[i].is_archived == false
          ) {
            channelList.push({
              id: content.channels[i].id,
              name: content.channels[i].name,
              purpose: content.channels[i].purpose.value
            });
          }
        }
      }
      //Write('\n final out ');
      Write(Stringify(channelList));
    }else if(parsedData.action == "createChannel") {
      var channelName = parsedData.channelName; 
      var is_private = parsedData.is_private; 
      var userId = parsedData.userId.join('%2C')
      var channelCreateURL = "https://slack.com/api/conversations.create" + "?name=" + channelName + "&is_private="+is_private;
      var headerNames = ["Authorization"];
      var headerValues = [parsedData.bearer];
      //Write('channelCreateURL' + channelCreateURL)
      var r = HTTP.Get(channelCreateURL, headerNames, headerValues);
      var content = Platform.Function.ParseJSON(r["Content"]);
      //Write('content - ' + Stringify(content));
      //Write('content ok - ' + content.ok);
      var channelId, respMsg;
      if(content.ok == true) { 
        channelId  = content.channel.id;
        var channelInviteURL = "https://slack.com/api/conversations.invite?channel="+channelId+"&users="+userId;
        var r2 = HTTP.Get(channelInviteURL, headerNames, headerValues);
        var content2 = Platform.Function.ParseJSON(r2["Content"]);
        //Write('content 2 - ' + Stringify(content2));
        //Write('content 2 ok - ' + content2.ok);
        if(content2.ok == true){
          var channelDesc = parsedData.channelDesc; 
          var channelDescURL = "https://slack.com/api/conversations.setPurpose?channel="+content.channel.id+"&purpose=" + channelDesc; 
          var r3 = HTTP.Get(channelDescURL, headerNames, headerValues);
          channelList.push({
            id: content.channel.id,
            name: content.channel.name,
            purpose: content.channel.purpose.value
          });
          Write(Stringify(channelList));
        }
      }else {
        Write(Stringify(content));
        break; 
      }
  } 
    else if (parsedData.journeyId) {
      if (parsedData.outArguments[0].userId[0] == "U") {
        //Notify USER
        var userChannelId;
        var conversationURL =
          "https://slack.com/api/conversations.open?prevent_creation=true&return_im=true&users=" +
          parsedData.outArguments[0].userId;
        // Write('\nconversationURL --> ' + conversationURL);
        var headerNames = ["Authorization"];
        var headerValues = ["Bearer " + parsedData.outArguments[0].xoxbToken];

  );

  var userList = [];

  try {
    var postBody = Platform.Request.GetPostData();
    var parsedData = Platform.Function.ParseJSON(postBody);
    if (parsedData.challenge) {

      var userListURL = "https://slack.com/api/users.list";

      //Write('Total users found - ' + Stringify(content.members.length));
      if (content.ok == true) {
        for (var i = 0; i < content.members.length; i++) {
          //Write('\n' + content.members[i].is_bot)
          if (!content.members[i].is_bot && content.members[i].id != 'USLACKBOT') {
            userList.push({
              id: content.members[i].id,
              real_name: content.members[i].profile.real_name,
              team: content.members[i].profile.team
            });
          }
        }
      }
      //Write('\n final out ');
      Write(Stringify(userList));
    }else if (parsedData.action == "getChannel") {
      var channelListURL = "https://slack.com/api/conversations.list";
      var headerNames = ["Authorization"];
      var headerValues = [parsedData.bearer];

          if (
            content.channels[i].is_channel == true &&
            content.channels[i].is_private == false &&
            content.channels[i].is_archived == false
          ) {
            channelList.push({
              id: content.channels[i].id,
              name: content.channels[i].name,
              purpose: content.channels[i].purpose.value
            });
          }
        }
      }
      //Write('\n final out ');
      Write(Stringify(channelList));
    }else if(parsedData.action == "createChannel") {
      var channelName = parsedData.channelName; 
      var is_private = parsedData.is_private; 
      var userId = parsedData.userId.join('%2C')
      var channelCreateURL = "https://slack.com/api/conversations.create" + "?name=" + channelName + "&is_private="+is_private;
      var headerNames = ["Authorization"];
      var headerValues = [parsedData.bearer];

      var r = HTTP.Get(channelCreateURL, headerNames, headerValues);
      var content = Platform.Function.ParseJSON(r["Content"]);
      //Write('content - ' + Stringify(content));
      //Write('content ok - ' + content.ok);
      var channelId, respMsg;
      if(content.ok == true) { 
        channelId  = content.channel.id;
        var channelInviteURL = "https://slack.com/api/conversations.invite?channel="+channelId+"&users="+userId;
        var r2 = HTTP.Get(channelInviteURL, headerNames, headerValues);
        var content2 = Platform.Function.ParseJSON(r2["Content"]);
        //Write('content 2 - ' + Stringify(content2));
        //Write('content 2 ok - ' + content2.ok);
        if(content2.ok == true){
          var channelDesc = parsedData.channelDesc; 
          var channelDescURL = "https://slack.com/api/conversations.setPurpose?channel="+content.channel.id+"&purpose=" + channelDesc; 
          var r3 = HTTP.Get(channelDescURL, headerNames, headerValues);
          channelList.push({
            id: content.channel.id,
            name: content.channel.name,
            purpose: content.channel.purpose.value
          });
          Write(Stringify(channelList));
        }
      }else {
        Write(Stringify(content));
        break; 
      }
  } 
    else if (parsedData.journeyId) {
      if (parsedData.outArguments[0].userId[0] == "U") {
        //Notify USER
        var userChannelId;
        var conversationURL =
          "https://slack.com/api/conversations.open?prevent_creation=true&return_im=true&users=" +
          parsedData.outArguments[0].userId;

        if (content.ok == true) {
          Write("{'messageSent': " + content.ok + "}");
        }
      }
    } else {
      Write('{"saved":"ok"}');
    }

    var de = "EventSubscription";
    var eventDE = DataExtension.Init(de);
    eventDE.Rows.Add({
      uuid: Platform.Function.GUID(),

  }
